title: BayBayin, Ancient Script of the Phillipines
description:
Baybayin ancient script of the Philippines, also known by it&#039;s Spanish name. Alibata.

This book, extremely rare (cannot even be bought on Amazon.com) is a great book to

learn how to reas, write, and get in touch with the native writing before the spanish

colonizers changed the written word to Latin characters.


The intro from the author:   This Manual is dedicated to future Filipinos who will have succeeded in breaking the colonial spell that kept them from being proud, authentic selves.
